Detailed Description

cvmx_slitb_msix::_table_addr

See SLI_MSIX()_TABLE_ADDR. These registers shadow the 128 physical MSIX RING entries. Each MAC accesses its RING entries using the PVF and a MSIX TABLE ADDR offset < 65.
